// Parse a `gh api repos/.../commits/<sha>/check-runs` response. Distinguishes
// API/parse failure (exit code != 0, timeout, empty/non-JSON body, missing
// fields) from "zero check_runs" so the merge-gate can give an accurate
// diagnosis.
//
